            <title>小米 Redmi 智能电视 X 2025 系列、米家立式学习灯 Pro 等新品 11 月 27 日发布</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/812/883.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/812/883.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 09:06:43 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2158026" rel="nofollow">Autumn_Dream</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2157400" rel="nofollow">顺势而为</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D795776" rel="nofollow">風見暉一</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1310370" rel="nofollow">偏科骚黄4100只眼</a> 的线索投递！</div>
